[[File:Dartflower.jpg|thumb|right|150px|A Dart flower]]
'''Dart flowers''' were tall [[Sentience/Legends|semi-sentient]] [[Plant/Legends|plants]] that grew on [[Dromund Kaas/Legends|Dromund Kaas]]. Either corrupted by the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]], or produced by [[Sith alchemy/Legends|Sith alchemy]], they were malevolent with hints of sentience.

Despite being stationary, they launched poisoned thorns against anyone who approached.

